fields.value: Extracted Data From: BHW Program Applicant and Award Data

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This submission includes publicly available data extracted in its original form. Please reference the Related Publication listed here for source and citation information

If you have questions about the underlying data stored here, please contact BHW regarding Program Applicant and Award Data. If you have questions or recommendations related to this metadata entry and extracted data, please contact the CAFE Data Management team at: climatecafe@bu.edu.

BHW’s Program Applicant Dashboards offer data tools and information related to the total number of eligible applicants and awardees for BHW’s National Health Service Corps (NHSC), Nurse Corps, Substance Use Disorder Treatment and Recovery (STAR), and Pediatric Specialty (PS) Loan Repayment Program (LRP) programs.

[Quote from: https://data.hrsa.gov/topics/health-workforce/applicant-dashboards]
